{"tid":1076052,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"太古城女子留遺書墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-03-24T14:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T15:40:28.000Z","uid":160807,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5cc367a3c30d2b9259fbe0a0df949b5ca240e0f0","tid":1076052,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T14:26:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190324/large/1553425856_f6ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190324%2Flarge%2F1553425856_f6ab.jpg&h=4c02b656&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【20:20】傷者送院後不治，警方撿獲一封遺書<br />\n<br />\n鰂魚涌太古城金星閣，下午5時許，保安發現一名43歲姓羅女子倒卧1樓簷篷上，懷疑她由高處墮下，於是報案。消防接報趕至，將墮樓女子救下，交由救護車送院搶救，惟抵院後證實不治。警方正在場調查。<br />\n<br />\nrip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190324/59407082\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190324%2F59407082&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6QEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=71bc87b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190324%2F59407082&h=b79a24af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190324/59407082</a>"},{"pid":"40c6ae104a8905845ac5f282fb7e74720052b0d0","tid":1076052,"uid":223757,"like":4,"dislike":26,"score":-22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T14:33:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"95e758ab6a2bdd6c4f33035ac757fc3e453a6215","tid":1076052,"uid":62822,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T14:33:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d8633152bf087f667330e6da15e6060b57bb0d1","tid":1076052,"uid":28831,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T14:34:16.000Z","msg":"太古城都要死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgm